SELECT "p"."Id", "p"."Content", "p"."CreatedAt", "p"."ImageData", "p"."UserId", "p"."Username", "c"."Id", "c"."Content", "c"."CreatedAt", "c"."PostId", "c"."UserId", "c"."Username"
